        =20
         <h2 id=3D"ACUBI-GUID-AB3FD6B8-F8F6-4371-8737-9C65699EF1A8" class=
=3D"sect2">About <span>Oracle Analytics</span> AI Agents
         </h2>
         <div class=3D"ind">
            <div>
               <p><span>Oracle Analytics</span> AI Agents enable you to def=
ine custom prompt instructions and incorporate organizational knowledge int=
o <span>Oracle Analytics</span> AI Assistant interactions.
               </p>
               <p>AI agents allow the <span>Oracle Analytics</span> AI Assi=
stant to interpret natural-language questions with greater accuracy and del=
iver more meaningful, context-aware insights. <span>Oracle Analytics</span>=
 AI Agents use Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) to enhance generative A=
I with enterprise data, enabling large language models (LLMs) to =E2=80=9Cl=
ook up=E2=80=9D relevant information before responding.<br><span class=3D"i=
mageleft"><img class=3D"imageleft" id=3D"GUID-AB3FD6B8-F8F6-4371-8737-9C656=
99EF1A8__IMAGE_ESW_TN4_RHC" height=3D"192" width=3D"1072" src=3D"https://do=
cs.oracle.com/en/cloud/paas/analytics-cloud/acubi/img/ai_agent_summary-png.=
png" alt=3D"Description of ai_agent_summary-png.png follows" title=3D"Descr=
iption of ai_agent_summary-png.png follows" longdesc=3D"https://docs.oracle=
.com/en/cloud/paas/analytics-cloud/acubi/img_text/ai_agent_summary-png.html=
"><br><a href=3D"https://docs.oracle.com/en/cloud/paas/analytics-cloud/acub=
i/img_text/ai_agent_summary-png.html">Description of the illustration ai_ag=
ent_summary-png.png</a></span><br></p>
               <p>AI agents provide reliable, context-rich insights by comb=
ining business data with tailored LLM instructions and private documentatio=
n. AI agents can help your teams move beyond static dashboards to interacti=
ve, conversational analytics that accelerate insight discovery and improve =
business performance.</p>
               <div class=3D"p">When you submit a question to an <span>Orac=
le Analytics</span> AI Agent:
                  <ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc;" id=3D"GUID-AB3FD6B8-=
F8F6-4371-8737-9C65699EF1A8__UL_QT4_WQ4_PHC">
                     <li>The agent automatically applies additional custom =
instructions created by the author, adding important context such as domain=
-specific definitions or guidance on preferred response formats.</li>
                     <li>A RAG process scans the selected enterprise docume=
nts configured by the author, enriching your prompt with focused, relevant =
information. The enhanced query is then processed by the <span>Oracle Analy=
tics</span> AI Assistant, which orchestrates the underlying LLM prompts to =
deliver a response that best reflects your intent and the available enterpr=
ise data.
                     </li>
                  </ul><br><div class=3D"imageleft"><img class=3D"imageleft=
" id=3D"GUID-AB3FD6B8-F8F6-4371-8737-9C65699EF1A8__IMAGE_KC4_XN4_RHC" heigh=
t=3D"270" width=3D"1072" src=3D"https://docs.oracle.com/en/cloud/paas/analy=
tics-cloud/acubi/img/ai_agent_workflow-png.png" alt=3D"Description of ai_ag=
ent_workflow-png.png follows" title=3D"Description of ai_agent_workflow-png=
.png follows" longdesc=3D"https://docs.oracle.com/en/cloud/paas/analytics-c=
loud/acubi/img_text/ai_agent_workflow-png.html"><br><a href=3D"https://docs=
.oracle.com/en/cloud/paas/analytics-cloud/acubi/img_text/ai_agent_workflow-=
png.html">Description of the illustration ai_agent_workflow-png.png</a></di=
v><br></div>
               <div class=3D"p">When you set up an AI agent in <span>Oracle=
 Analytics</span>, you=E2=80=99ll configure four primary components:
                  <ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc;" id=3D"GUID-AB3FD6B8-=
F8F6-4371-8737-9C65699EF1A8__OL_VRS_M2R_QHC">
                     <li><span class=3D"bold">Dataset</span> =E2=80=93 The =
