                     <li><span class=3D"bold">Supplemental Instructions</sp=
an> =E2=80=93 Custom guidance that shapes how the <span>Oracle Analytics</s=
pan> AI Assistant interprets user intent and formulates responses. These in=
structions influence the <span>Oracle Analytics</span> AI Assistant=E2=80=
=99s reasoning and behavior. For example, by defining business terminology,=
 specifying fiscal logic, outlining naming conventions, or clarifying domai=
n rules. In essence, they teach the <span>Oracle Analytics</span> AI Assist=
ant to think and communicate in your organization=E2=80=99s language. Every=
thing included here is passed directly to the AI without preprocessing. See=
